FL,393,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39202
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F392A1777287772
OL,3,CMother of murdered teenager demands
OL,4,C'urgent' meeting with PM
OL,6,FIn a strongly worded letter sent on
OL,7,Fbehalf of multiple affected families,
OL,8,FEsther warned that delays in
OL,9,Fgovernment action are continuing to
OL,10,F"cost young lives."
OL,12,FHer appeal follows a meeting between
OL,13,Fthe Prime Minister and senior
OL,14,Fexecutives from tech giants including
OL,15,FMeta, TikTok, and X (formerly Twitter)
OL,16,Fearlier this month.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/8
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,393,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39203
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F392A1777287772
OL,3,CMother of murdered teenager demands
OL,4,C'urgent' meeting with PM
OL,6,FAhead of the meeting, Sir Keir said:
OL,7,F"I will take whatever steps necessary
OL,8,Fto keep children safe online. Today is
OL,9,Fabout making sure social media
OL,10,Fcompanies step up and take
OL,11,Fresponsibility.
OL,13,F"The consequences of failing to act
OL,14,Fare stark. We owe it to parents, and
OL,15,Fto the next generation, to put
OL,16,Fchildren's safety first ` because they
OL,17,Fwon't forgive us if we don't."
OL,26,@oD@AOUuD@AOUyD@^O]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/8
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,393,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39204
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F392A1777287772
OL,3,CMother of murdered teenager demands
OL,4,C'urgent' meeting with PM
OL,6,FEsther argued that while engagement
OL,7,Fwith the tech industry is necessary,
OL,8,Fthe voices of those who have suffered
OL,9,Fthe "devastating consequences" of
OL,10,Fonline harms is "equally important."
OL,12,F"I am writing to request an urgent
OL,13,Fmeeting with you alongside bereaved
OL,14,Ffamilies who have been profoundly
OL,15,Faffected by the harms associated with
OL,16,Fonline platforms," she wrote.
OL,18,F"We are incredibly disappointed to
OL,19,Flearn that you invited social media
OL,20,Fcompanies to discuss this issue prior
OL,21,Fto meeting with families like ours.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/8
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,393,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39205
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F392A1777287772
OL,3,CMother of murdered teenager demands
OL,4,C'urgent' meeting with PM
OL,6,F"While we understand the importance f
OL,7,Fengaging with industry, it is of equal
OL,8,Fimportance that you hear directly from
OL,9,Fthose who have experienced the
OL,10,Fdevastating consequences associated
OL,11,Fwith online platforms."
OL,13,FGhey, who has become a leading
OL,14,Fadvocate for mental health and mobile
OL,15,Fphone reform, reminded the Prime
OL,16,FMinister of their previous discussions
OL,17,Fregarding youth mental health before
OL,18,Fhe took office.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/8
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,393,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39206
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F392A1777287772
OL,3,CMother of murdered teenager demands
OL,4,C'urgent' meeting with PM
OL,6,FShe urged him to return to that "care
OL,7,Fand attention" now that he holds the
OL,8,Fpower to legislate.
OL,10,F"We may not have the financial
OL,11,Finfluence of large corporations, but
OL,12,Fwhat we do have is an unwavering
OL,13,Fdetermination to ensure no child or
OL,14,Fparent has to endure the pain and
OL,15,Fsuffering we experienced", she said.
OL,17,F"We want to share our stories with you
OL,18,Fto make clear why it's is important
OL,19,Fthat the government urgently takes
OL,20,Fmeaningful action."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/8
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
