PN,39207
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F392A1777287772
OL,3,CMother of murdered teenager demands
OL,4,C'urgent' meeting with PM
OL,6,FThe letter concluded with a stark
OL,7,Fwarning: "Every day we delay is
OL,8,Fanother day that our children are
OL,9,Fexposed to the harms associated with
OL,10,Fonline platforms, and more lives are
OL,11,Flost."
OL,13,FEsther campaigns for child-safe
OL,14,Fsmartphones that restrict access to
OL,15,Fsocial media for under-16s, software
OL,16,Fthat flags concerning search terms to
OL,17,Fparents and mindfulness training in
OL,18,Fschools through her 'Peace in Mind'
OL,19,Fcampaign.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/8
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
